DOC.brief_summary: This study will evaluate the safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics (PK) of AGN-223575 in healthy subjects.
DOC.brief_title: A Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics (PK) Study of AGN-223575 in Healthy Subjects
DOC.criteria: Weight at least 110 lbs Use of contact lenses within 14 days, or planned use during the study Use of any ocular eye medications within 30 days, or anticipated use during the study Anticipated use of any artificial tears product during the study
